data.description: Nestled inside of Lakeview Retreat on the corner lot, this stunning 2 story, 4bedroom/3.5 bathroom home is a must see! With no shortage of space this home is ideal for anyone looking for their forever home. Two car garage, spacious backyard and modern conveniences such as smart home security and solar panels just to name a few.  Come home to an open concept floor plan, large living area great for entertaining and the kitchen is equipped with granite counter tops, an island with space for additional seating and stainless steel appliances. Schedule a tour today! Please send all offers to agent.
